WEBVTT

00:00:01.530 --> 00:00:03.431
er hot nisht gekent arbetn.

00:00:03.555 --> 00:00:06.485
ven undz ze'mir gekumen fun Rusland hot men undz gezogt

00:00:06.525 --> 00:00:10.788
az efsher er iz shtark, a a groyse astme hot er gehat.

00:00:11.672 --> 00:00:16.419
un dos harts iz im geven nisht sh- nisht gut.

00:00:16.419 --> 00:00:19.480
ober nisht azoy vayt az in dort hot er gehat eyn fakt.

00:00:20.532 --> 00:00:27.495
nor di astme hot im shtark gemutshet. er hot nu dort in Rusland hot er zitserdikerheyt geshlofn.

00:00:27.838 --> 00:00:31.899
nisht geshlofn nor gehust di gantse nakht. oyf fir kishn.

00:00:33.002 --> 00:00:39.797
un ven ze'mir gekumen aher oyf Izrael, in Lud hot men undz gezogt az undz darf'mir nemen nor Ber Sheva.

00:00:40.663 --> 00:00:42.564
Ber Sheva ober Arad.

00:00:43.093 --> 00:00:48.757
mayn man's UNK hot do a bruder gehat, ze'mir gekumen tsun im, er iz oykh befor aroysgekumen.

00:00:50.772 --> 00:00:57.262
un ze'mir gekumen aher oyf Ber Sheva, in tsvey vokhn, in a khoydesh arum, iz im fariber dos husn.

00:00:57.336 --> 00:01:00.640
DA? er iz gevorn in gantsn an anderer mentsh.

00:01:00.640 --> 00:01:02.572
m'hot im arayngenumen in shpitol arayn,

00:01:02.572 --> 00:01:06.949
m'hot ongehoybn tsu heyln, m'hot ibergebitn di gantse meditsinen,

00:01:07.005 --> 00:01:10.807
un di gantse vaser iz fun im arop.

00:01:10.807 --> 00:01:17.495
dort hobn zey gezogt mir az er vet nisht oyshaltn, vayl bayn im iz di gantse leber tsevashn.

00:01:17.873 --> 00:01:24.836
vifl hobn geven do in Izrael hot keyn keyn eyn dokter nisht gezogt az im epes mit di leber. DA.

00:01:25.382 --> 00:01:27.603
iz nayn yor hot er nokh do gelebt.

00:01:29.263 --> 00:01:32.126
UNK

00:01:31.845 --> 00:01:33.239
UNK

00:01:32.976 --> 00:01:37.121
UNK

00:01:37.870 --> 00:01:45.899
nu undz ho'mir demolts gornisht gekent fir UNK. ober az epes andersht neyn.

00:01:45.899 --> 00:01:53.946
nor undz hot men oykhet gemutshet nayn khadoshim. undz ze'mir nisht geven nisht keyn partiner, un nisht keyn shum min problemen, proste arbetorer.

00:01:54.643 --> 00:01:59.311
hot men undz gemutshet nayn khadoshim, m'hot undz gegebn UNK.

00:02:00.195 --> 00:02:05.791
iz ales geven tsen tog, in der tsen tog hot men zikh gedarft tsamnemen. nu m'hot zikh tsugegreyt foroys.

00:02:06.945 --> 00:02:09.116
nor mit mayn man iz geven shver.

00:02:10.708 --> 00:02:14.060
UNK

00:02:13.628 --> 00:02:14.415
UNK

00:02:15.147 --> 00:02:16.018
UNK

00:02:16.750 --> 00:02:18.229
UNK

00:02:18.336 --> 00:02:23.341
vi ken ikh forn mit a krankn mentsh? UNK Izrael efsher.

00:02:23.533 --> 00:02:28.271
der UNK hot men undz gefregt etlekhe mol tsi undz vil'mir nisht forn ergets andersh.

00:02:28.271 --> 00:02:34.749
nu vu hin? mayn man hot shvesterkinder in Amerike, nu yeder far zikh.

00:02:36.797 --> 00:02:39.418
er hot nisht gevolt iber hoypt forn az er iz krank,

00:02:39.418 --> 00:02:42.700
mir ho'mir gezogt undz e'mir beyde arbetn. ikh un mayn zun e'mir arbetn.

00:02:42.700 --> 00:02:48.890
mayn zun hot opgedint, afile er iz gekumen a PEREROSTOK, er iz shoyn geven a tsvey un tsvontsik yor.

00:02:49.318 --> 00:02:51.961
dort iz er nisht geven a soldat, der yingerer.

00:02:53.807 --> 00:02:58.526
un undz hot di ARMIYA geholfn a bisl vayl m'hot nisht bakumen keyn pensye.

00:02:58.752 --> 00:03:01.176
tsvey yor hot er nisht bakumen keyn pensye.

00:03:01.890 --> 00:03:07.824
nokh di tsvey yor hot men undz gegebn. er hot gezogt az di krankeyt hot er fun Rusland gebrengt. nisht do.

00:03:08.370 --> 00:03:10.186
undz iz geven zeyer shver.

00:03:10.817 --> 00:03:13.629
hitst iz oykh nisht gring, nor demolts iz geven nokh shverer.

00:03:15.087 --> 00:03:17.224
UNK

00:03:16.335 --> 00:03:17.696
UNK

00:03:19.677 --> 00:03:22.337
UNK

00:03:23.187 --> 00:03:26.099
nu dos shraybt zikh oykhet ales? DA.

00:03:26.342 --> 00:03:31.499
yo, avade bin ikh tsufridn. vos het ikh geton in Rusland aleyn?

00:03:31.894 --> 00:03:36.208
het gelebt oyf der pensye, dort do ken ikh oyslebn oyf der pensye, ober dort ken ikh nisht.

00:03:38.526 --> 00:03:41.338
s'hot hob ikh do nisht gearbet, ikh hob nor TAPELET,

00:03:41.698 --> 00:03:45.303
vayl ikh hob nisht gekent arbetn, un ikh hob bakumen BITUACH LEUMI.

00:03:47.233 --> 00:03:48.948
UNK

00:03:49.022 --> 00:03:49.691
NIET.

00:03:50.575 --> 00:03:53.303
UNK

00:03:53.325 --> 00:03:55.631
UNK

00:03:55.654 --> 00:03:57.842
UNK

00:03:58.742 --> 00:03:59.799
UNK

00:03:58.759 --> 00:03:59.883
PLASIBO.

00:04:00.666 --> 00:04:08.625
nu yo UNK.

00:04:09.660 --> 00:04:12.624
UNK

00:04:13.035 --> 00:04:14.497
UNK

00:04:14.335 --> 00:04:15.831
UNK

00:04:15.415 --> 00:04:17.535
UNK

00:04:18.822 --> 00:04:19.778
UNK

00:04:20.358 --> 00:04:23.542
UNK

00:04:24.392 --> 00:04:25.567
UNK

00:04:26.923 --> 00:04:28.857
UNK

00:04:28.948 --> 00:04:29.870
UNK

00:04:30.197 --> 00:04:34.764
UNK

00:04:37.825 --> 00:04:39.003
UNK

00:04:43.258 --> 00:04:45.159
deys iz mayne eltern.

00:04:45.975 --> 00:04:49.529
deys bild iz gemakht gevorn in finef un draysiker yor.

00:04:50.194 --> 00:04:56.477
mayn tate heyst Goydl, Yitskhok Leyb oyf yidish hot er geheysn.

00:04:56.477 --> 00:05:01.731
di mame heyst Khane. di familye zire, di meydlshe, Tabak.

00:05:02.462 --> 00:05:04.683
undz ho'mir gevoynt in Rakhev.

00:05:09.364 --> 00:05:14.735
deys iz mayn dokument vos ikh hob bakumen funem Roytn Kreyts fun Daytshland,

00:05:14.735 --> 00:05:17.019
vu ikh bin geven in konts-lager.

00:05:23.691 --> 00:05:26.807
TAK deys iz der dokument oyf der tsveyter zayt.

00:05:27.353 --> 00:05:32.797
deys iz oykhet vu pinktlekh geshribn vu ikh bin geven in konts-lager, velkhe pletser.

00:05:34.018 --> 00:05:34.420
shoy-
